title: Charming 2BR/2BA Sunnyvale Condo - Available Now!
posting_body: ['Charming 2BR/2BA Sunnyvale Condo - Available Now!', '- IF YOU ARE INTERESTED APPLY ASAP', 'FIRST COME, FIRST SERVE !', 'Available Now!', 'Unit Information:', '-Newer Carpet in both bedrooms and storage room!', '-Newer linoleum flooring in master bathroom!', '-2BR/2BA second floor unit', '-Kitchen offers breakfast counter, gas range, built-in microwave,', '-Refrigerator, dishwasher, range/oven and microwave and ample storage space', '-Separate dining room accommodates a full size table and chairs', '-Inside laundry room with full-size side-by-side washer/dryer', '-Master bedroom offers built-in closet systems, mirrored wardrobes and en suite', 'bath', '-Second bedroom has large walk-in closet with built-in closet system', '-Master bath with all tub/shower stall, granite counter top, fixtures and flooring', '-Guest bath with granite counter top, fixtures and flooring', '-Storage room with built-in shelves provide additional storage space', '-Window coverings throughout', '-Front door and back door entrances; back door leads to exterior one car parking garage', '-Private balcony with tree shading for additional privacy.', '-Water and garbage included', '-Central heating and air conditioning included', 'Location:', "Close to Hwy 101, Caltrain, VTA, downtown Sunnyvale, LinkedIn offices, future Apple offices, Google campuses and new Levi's 49er Stadium", 'Common Area Amenities', '-Lovely well-maintained grounds', '-Swimming pool with showers and restroom', "-Children's play area and walking paths", '-On-site security', 'Parking', '-One detached garage #160, and one outside homeowner parking space (parking tag must be displayed)', 'Don’t miss this opportunity!']
